Package: ssh.utils
Title: Execute local and remote system commands.
Version: 1.0
Author: Sergei Izrailev
Maintainer: Sergei Izrailev <sizrailev@collective.com>
Description: This package provides utility functions for system command
    execution, both locally and remotely using ssh/scp.
    The command output is captured and provided to the caller.
URL: http://github.com/collectivemedia/ssh.utils
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.3),
    stringr,
    fork
License: Apache License (== 2.0)
